&lt;h2 id="advanced-section-features">Advanced Section Features&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Hugo sections provide powerful features for content organization:&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="custom-section-templates">Custom Section Templates&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>You can create custom templates for each section by placing them in &lt;code>layouts/SECTION/&lt;/code>:&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>layouts/articles/list.html&lt;/code> - for &lt;code>/articles/&lt;/code> page&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>layouts/articles/single.html&lt;/code> - for individual articles&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3 id="section-variables">Section Variables&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>In templates, you can access section-specific data:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#1f2328">{{&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">.&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#1f2328">Section&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">}}&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#57606a">// &amp;#34;articles&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#1f2328">{{&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">.&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#1f2328">Type&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">}}&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#57606a">// content type&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#1f2328">{{&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">.&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#1f2328">Pages&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">}}&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#57606a">// all pages in section&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#1f2328">{{&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">.&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#1f2328">RegularPages&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#1f2328">}}&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#57606a">// only regular pages&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="taxonomies-per-section">Taxonomies per Section&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>Each section can have its own taxonomies (tags, categories) with independent organization.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>